import React from 'react'
import Profile from './Profile'
import References from './References'
import {BrowserRouter as Router,
    Switch,
    Route,
    Link} from 'react-router-dom'

function Body() {
    return (
        <Router className="body">

            <Switch>
                <Route path="/">
                    <Profile />
                </Route>
                <Route path="">
                    <References/>
                </Route>
            </Switch>
            
        </Router>
    )
}

export default Body
